### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###Recuperar todos los ticketTypes (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crear un ticketType (primer ticket type del evento se activa autom√°ticamente)
# @name createTicketType1
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "ticketTypeName": "Early Bird",
    "price": 3500,
    "maxQuantity": 100,
    "event": 1,
    "sortOrder": 1
}

### Crear un segundo ticketType (queda como PENDING en la cola)
# @name createTicketType2
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "ticketTypeName": "General",
    "price": 5000,
    "maxQuantity": 200,
    "event": 1,
    "sortOrder": 2
}

### Crear un tercer ticketType (queda como PENDING en la cola)
# @name createTicketType3
POST {{baseUrl}}/ticketType
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "ticketTypeName": "VIP",
    "price": 8000,
    "maxQuantity": 50,
    "event": 1,
    "sortOrder": 3
}

### ID del ticket type creado
@ticketTypeId = {{createTicketType1.response.body.data.id}}

### Obtener un ticketType por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Cerrar el ticket type activo (transfiere tickets restantes al siguiente y lo activa)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}/close
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Actualizar nombre y precio de un ticketType
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "ticketTypeName": "Early Bird Promo",
    "price": 3000
}

### Actualizar sortOrder
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "sortOrder": 5
}

### Eliminar un ticketType
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/ticketType/{{ticketTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
